com.irurueta.server.commons.image

Enum Flash

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Flash>
      • com.irurueta.server.commons.image.Flash
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Flash>

    public enum Flash
extends Enum<Flash>
    Enumerator indicating flash modes of EXIF data contained in an image file.
